/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format_id": "4", "format": "4 - 750x1333"}], "title": "Video by monica.sophiaa2", "description": "#thoughts", "duration": 46.1, "timestamp": 1769992285, "uploader_id": "79920993663", "uploader": "Monica Sophia", "channel": "monica.sophiaa2", "like_count": 906, "comment_count": 52, "comments": [{"author": "richardgoesfast", "author_id": "12281401023", "id": "18078072122564611", "text": "That is a really great insight well stated. Thank you for this", "timestamp": 1774829097}, {"author": "ashyayman", "author_id": "582415263", "id": "17955538311093418", "text": "100 percent! ❤️", "timestamp": 1774650832}, {"author": "adamarnelson", "author_id": "53792670243", "id": "18078510551545813", "text": "excellent", "timestamp": 1774479380}, {"author": "dhirraj29", "author_id": "49121669436", "id": "18095408888295955", "text": "Loved it \nThanks so much", "timestamp": 1774073927}, {"author": "matthew_amswb", "author_id": "69411658901", "id": "18340821874212424", "text": "I think you're half right on that. It doesn't collapse it into a single reality. Observation pushes it into infinite other realities. None of which you're prepared for because your vantage point is limited. I consider this the other day when I considered whether or not God was real, and if so, how. We see this by both the physical and spiritual representations of God. In the old Greek and Hebrew essentially rails for the narrow path. God is described as a particle in the old Greek. So properly when viewed in right light, the Bible and science complement each other they don’t argue. One is simply a description of the other, and if the description doesn’t fit, then your math is wrong.", "timestamp": 1773712118}, {"author": "el_gorgo", "author_id": "6077538130", "id": "17927900055236823", "text": "And the fact is none of the quantum physicist have been able to define \"observation\". The argument still rages on.", "timestamp": 1772917951}, {"author": "murphytjames", "author_id": "67440458071", "id": "18564020383057463", "text": "Reality is constant and unchangeable", "timestamp": 1772317570}, {"author": "murphytjames", "author_id": "67440458071", "id": "18154519582437569", "text": "It's not reality. It's illusion.", "timestamp": 1772317551}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/625379412_17852494419665664_8087755907415730877_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p640x640_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi43MjB4MTI4MC5zZHIuZjgyNzg3LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFFoZ_1QrVyPjI8mBkI8bKZsPZ_1NO_METT7xXPzw7BFUZzAeL14lE1rehHxWqTI_I&_nc_ohc=N-3vXtWwrx4Q7kNvwGu0wn8&_nc_gid=SqGis1iaL7hgj-adS6wbLA&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af3WLve8coJE2LdZaZZqgQfw31CFiyimFHVppnPTrQO8cg&oe=69D4CEEF&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1137, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1137"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/625379412_17852494419665664_8087755907415730877_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi43MjB4MTI4MC5zZHIuZjgyNzg3LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFFoZ_1QrVyPjI8mBkI8bKZsPZ_1NO_METT7xXPzw7BFUZzAeL14lE1rehHxWqTI_I&_nc_ohc=N-3vXtWwrx4Q7kNvwGu0wn8&_nc_gid=SqGis1iaL7hgj-adS6wbLA&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0JM8JQ1NHIvD_vVrVjwkxsqEtlOkqYPB853gZ0LuJvdA&oe=69D4CEEF&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1333, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1333"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/625379412_17852494419665664_8087755907415730877_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi43MjB4MTI4MC5zZHIuZjgyNzg3LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninsta